extends ../layouts/default
block content
  h1 How many characters are in this string?

  p Sometimes I just need to get the length of a string. 

  div
    label(for="InputString")
      | Enter a string to calculate it's length
      span#Results.hide &nbsp;(
        strong#StringLength
        | )
    textarea(id="InputString" rows="5")
  div
    small This utility uses only front end JavaScript no data is sent to the server.

  script(src='dist/js/tools/strlen.js')

